        <title>SAM Crack Segmentation Experiments: Prompt Point Strategies and Performance Evaluation</title>
        <link>https://whhong-research.github.io/en/p/sam-crack-segmentation-experiments-prompt-point-strategies-and-performance-evaluation/</link>
